        <purpose>Small SpaceFOM-inspired FOM for RTI/federate testing with reference frames, entities, sensors, and execution modes.</purpose>
        <applicationDomain>Space systems distributed simulation testbed</applicationDomain>
        <description>Defines execution configuration, reference frames, physical/dynamical entities, interfaces, sensors, and tracks.</description>
        <useLimitation>Depends on HLAx_Base.xml. It is not a formal SpaceFOM replacement or conformance claim.</useLimitation>
        <useHistory>Initial v0.1 draft generated from HLA-X planning conversation.</useHistory>
